### From Masse

Document
. "base archetype"
. object instance or DB record -- includes fields with values and links to related resources
. use singular names
 -- e.g., api.soccer.restapi.org/leagues/seattle

Collection
. server-managed directory of resources
. plural noun
 -- e.g., api.soccer.restapi.org/leagues

Store
. "client-managed resource repository"
. plural
. e.g., /users/1234/favorites/alonso
 -- 'favorites' is the store in this case

Controller
. procedural resource -- e.g., an executable function
. actions that can't be mapped to CRUD operation
. verb
